# Vue Architecture Boundaries

- Keep `src/views/` focused on presentation and light orchestration.
- Put reusable contracts, protocol calls, and shared logic into `src/lib/` or `src/types/`.
- Do not build system-level governance or agent orchestration directly inside page components.
- When touching Harness UI, preserve its role as a debug/observation surface rather than turning it into the only workflow.
